    <p>
      <b>AcRemote access to a computer</b>
    </p>
    <p>
      Access to a&#160;remote computer,&#160;mount a share&#160; and&#160;run a program:
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>psexec -u user -p password \\computer &quot;cmd /c net use z: \\local_ip\share &amp; x:\program.exe&quot;</i></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      Umount a share:
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>psexec -u user -p password \\computer net use z: /delete </i></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/fr-fr/sysinternals">http://technet.microsoft.com/fr-fr/sysinternals</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      PAExec (PsExec FORK) <a href="https://github.com/poweradminllc/PAExec">https://github.com/poweradminllc/PAExec</a>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
