    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="hps">To capture</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">the first page of</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">physical memory</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0; </span><span class="hps">(page</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">0)</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">containing the memory</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">area</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0; </span><span class="hps">in which the</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">BIOS</span><span lang="en" class="" id="result_box">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">keyboard buffer</span><span>:</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font face="Courier New" color="#ff0000"><i>win32dd.exe -d -t 1 d:\mem.raw</i></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
