<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b>DD disque</b>
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Install the JDK : <a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html">http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html</a><o p="#DEFAULT"></o>
      </li>
      <li>
        Install Android studio (check OS version) : <a href="http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html">http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html</a><o p="#DEFAULT"></o>
      </li>
      <li>
        Enable USB debugging (If the option is hidden, click 7 time on&#160;the serial number&#160;in the options menu) and connect the phone
      </li>
      <li>
        &#160;Go to directory: <font face="Arial,sans-serif">C:\Users\XXX\AppData\Local\Android\Android-sdk\platform-tools\</font>
      </li>
      <li>
        Check if the phone is detected : <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New" size="2"><b>adb device</b></font>
      </li>
      <li>
        &#160;Start shell adb : <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New" size="2"><b>adb shell</b></font>
      </li>
      <li>
        Get root : <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New" size="2"><b>su</b></font>
      </li>
      <li>
        Check the mount : <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New" size="2"><b>mount</b></font>
      </li>
      <li>
        Make a copy of the mount point to the SD card <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New" size="2"><b>/mnt/ExtSdCard/</b></font>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><b>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;dd if=...sdcc-1/by-name/userdata of=/mnt/ExtSdCard/output.raw</b></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
