<node CREATED="1352467503511" ID="ID_444271130" MODIFIED="1470637221972">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b>List the files</b>
    </p>
    <p>
      For Unix/Linux, extract all the file with MD5 hash:
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>md5deep -r &gt; resultat_sha256.txt </i></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      For Unix/Linux, extract all the file with SHA256 hash:
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>sha256deep -r &gt; resultat_sha256.txt</i></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      All the files with ACL.
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>find / -exec ls -al {} \; &gt; liste_all_file.txt</i></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      For Windows without ACL :
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>dir c:\ /N /ON /Q /S</i></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      For Windows with ACL:
    </p>
    <p>
      DACLchk (ForensicToolkit) <a href="http://www.mcafee.com/us/downloads/free-tools/forensic-toolkit.aspx">http://www.mcafee.com/us/downloads/free-tools/forensic-toolkit.aspx</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>DACLchk.exe C:\ -d &gt; liste_all_files.txt</i></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      Dirlist <a href="http://www.mitec.cz/dirlist.html">http://www.mitec.cz/dirlist.html</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      WindowsDACLEnumProject <a href="https://github.com/nccgroup/WindowsDACLEnumProject">https://github.com/nccgroup/WindowsDACLEnumProject</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      EnumDirectory <a href="http://omni.a.free.fr/app.html">http://omni.a.free.fr/app.html</a>&#160;:
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#ff0000" face="Courier New"><i>EnumDirectory_V2.0.exe -R c:\ &gt; liste_all_files.txt</i></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
