    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#0000ff">HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\%Application% </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="#0000ff">HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\%Application%</font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="hps">Tool</span><span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="en">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">for extracting</span><span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="en">&#xa0;</span><span class="hps">data</span><span>:</span>
